content.description: Sit start with right hand on low side pull crimp to the right of the arete, left hand on low flat slanted crimp. Work up using side pull crimps on both sides of the arete to gain some nice holds for an easy top out. If you can figure out how to get off the ground, this has some fun moves!
content.location: Arete to the right of Doo Doo Brown.

content.description: Sds down and left on this block and continue up and right. Prepare to mantle through some branches.
content.location: left most line on the block to the right of the Flat Head boulder. Is directly to the right of the tree near the Flat Head Arete.

content.description: Stand start matched on crimps and move up using right hand pinch and left hand sidepulls to work up to the top out. This is the stand to what could be a very difficult sit start on the overhanging face of the flat head boulder.
content.location: left most line on the overhanging face of the flat head boulder.

content.description: Sds and find a way to climb up into the stand start, continue to the top. This is an interesting enough line that is pretty bare on the bottom, feels hard.
content.location: Start low and left on the overhanging face of the Flat Head boulder.

content.description: Start as low as possible on the overhanging arete of the flat head boulder. Climb up and left and top out.
content.location: This is the rounded arete of the Flat Head boulder, just to the right of the Flat Head stand.

content.description: Despite its short stature, this is a worthy problem if you're in the area. Sit start with hands on side pull crimps to the right and left of the arete (bunchy!) Go straight up the arete to the flat top out. The grade is a guess as it might vary depending on your height and flexibility. A stand start can also be done with left hand on flat sloper to the left of the arete and right hand on low side pull crimp (V3ish?).
content.protection: 1 pad. A spotter might be nice for the top out.
content.location: Short arete to the right of Path of Most Resistance.
